Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:08.25,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Today we have two special guests with a very special announcement!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:11.94,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Everypony, welcome the head of the Equestria Games,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.70,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Miss Harshwhinny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:18.73,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:23.41,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm sure, you all know about Equestria Games,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:27.13,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,where ponies from all over the land compete for glory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.60,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,in various athletic pursuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:31.72,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:35.05,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,now you littlest ones will have the chance to compete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.53,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,for a weighty responsibility of your very own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:38.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Tell them the fun part!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:47.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:49.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,All you gotta do is show Miss Harshwhinny
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:52.45,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,the coolest, most spectacular, most rocking routine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:54.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and you're going to the Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:57.30,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, who's going to be the lucky ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:00:59.37,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:00.87,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:02.42,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:04.01,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:11.27,Snips,,0,0,0,,Hey, it could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:56.52,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, the winning team gets to carry the Ponyville flag in the Equestria games!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are gonna love this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:04.64,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Miss Dash, will you please curb your overenthusiastic outbursts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:08.31,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Now then, let me be clear on the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:10.96,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,You, ponies, will form teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:14.28,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Each team will create their own flag carrying routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:16.92,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Everypony will be judged on grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:19.08,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,style and originality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:24.14,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,There's a most complicated scoring system which I will elaborate on about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:24.84,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Firstly…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:27.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Aw, get to the nitty-gritty later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:28.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Tell 'em the important stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Like who's the coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:32.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:33.63,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.94,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And you know why I'm qualified to coach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:41.36,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Guess who carried the Cloudsdale flag in the Games when she was a little filly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:42.33,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:44.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I burst into the stadium,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:50.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,spreading my wings, the flag flapping in the breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:54.57,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I did tricks with that flag the likes of which nopony saw before
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and nopony's seen since!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:03.08,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Professionalism, Ms. Dash. I must insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.93,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,If you want to keep your job as coach of these ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:08.75,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,you must maintain a professional attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.82,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,and keep your emotions in check!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:15.53,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Am I making myself absolutely, one hundred percent crystal clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:21.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yes, Miss Hearshwhinny. You know, "professionalism" is my middle name,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Professionalism Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:28.13,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Well, in three days time, Ms. Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:32.00,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,will accompany anypony competing to the Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.99,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,where you will demonstrate your routines for me and the other judges,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:39.59,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,who will judge you very professionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:43.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yes. Quite, quite correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:48.32,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, get ready to train, and train hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:52.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,because I know this opening ceremony is the single most important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:55.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,that will ever happen in your young lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But I know you're up for the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:59.18,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And so am I!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Meet me after school tomorrow at fifteen hundred hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.97,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And show me your flag-carrying skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I am outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Professionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:16.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,See how professionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.19,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Ponies! The most important thing is this:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:23.40,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Your routine is to show what your town means to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:26.03,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,So, do Ponyville proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.40,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Work hard, be bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.64,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Wow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:31.67,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,That is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:39.38,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So what do you say we come up with the perfect routine and win this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.88,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'd say that's rootin'-tootin' terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.42,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,But there's one problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.80,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I bet every pony in class is planning to compete!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:50.81,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Listen. Some pony in our class is gonna carry that flag,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.40,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,so it might as well be us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.89,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Crusaders, are you in or are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.31,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Cause I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.55,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.36,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Me three!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:03.53,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,All right, the winning routine needs to show what's important about Ponyville, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:04.22,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:07.54,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So, what's special about Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:09.51,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,It's… It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:13.64,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:17.25,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,It's a place where different kinds of pomnies live together as friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.46,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Earth ponies like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.17,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Unicorns like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.91,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And pegasi like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:26.14,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So somehow we've gotta figure out a way to show that in the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:27.81,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We're gonna need a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.64,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And lotta hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.72,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And whole bunch of practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:32.73,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,But take it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:35.34,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,We just be little ponies, but
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:37.38,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,we have hearts as strong as horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:49.66,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We're the toughest little ponies in town
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:54.54,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Got the moves, got the mojo, no harder working ponies around
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:57.34,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We are a trio, work as a team
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:02.33,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We'll be the first ponies out on the flag-waving scene
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:12.98,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We get going when the going gets tough
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:16.81,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We know our very best is just never enough
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:20.98,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We're kinda short, but so what? We don't get defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:24.83,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We could take a little break, but we don't need it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:27.94,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got hearts as strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:31.88,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got hearts as strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:35.96,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got hearts as strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:42.07,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got hea-a-a-arts, hearts strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:52.39,Somepony,,0,0,0,,When we put our minds together, we can achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:56.27,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We're the Cutie Mark Crusaders, and you should believe
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:00.15,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got determination to represent the nation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:03.05,Somepony,,0,0,0,,For the win
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:07.11,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got hearts as strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:10.99,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got hearts as strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:15.15,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got hearts as strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:19.16,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And we're flying to win as we gallop to glory
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:22.18,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We can conquer any challenge we're in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:29.06,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got hearts, hearts strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:33.26,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Hearts strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:47.97,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,If that's the best you've got, we're going to win for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:52.41,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,We alrady have the most refined routine planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:57.79,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,That's absolutely sure to crush everyone else and I mean crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:01.02,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,But we are winners and we have our hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.19,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Sure. But you know what you don't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.92,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Your cutie-marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:10.76,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Blank-flanks! Blank-flanks! Blank-flanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:12.73,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What does have that to do with flag-carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:18.09,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Having cutie-mark-less ponies represent Ponyville would be unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:22.44,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,And we, of course, already have our cutie-marks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:25.20,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,so we know who's gonna be in a winners circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:28.70,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Listen, you two! Cutie-marks or no cutie-marks, you'll see,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:31.76,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,the Crusaders are gonna carry that flag in the Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:35.49,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,May the best ponies win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:36.64,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Game on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Show me what you've got, Cutie-Mark Crusaders! And make it good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:50.27,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.87,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Now, that's just a little something that we threw together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:56.26,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,It's not perfect yet, not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:09:01.86,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Let's watch the Cutie-Mark Goofsaders do their sad little routing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.86,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,There's gonna be a hot mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:09.79,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Since the dawn of recorded time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:13.10,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,in one town of amazing amazingness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:16.76,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,three types of pony coesxist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.98,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We are earth ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.66,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We are unicorns!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.18,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,We are pegasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:27.12,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And the town where friendship reigns is our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:32.07,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Now welcome to the stadium the flag of the place we love best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:40.87,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Ponyville forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:40.87,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Ponyville forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:40.87,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Ponyville forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.07,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,It's kind of work in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.32,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So, what did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:52.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That! Was! Amazi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wait. Hold on now. Gotta stay calm, cool, and collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.64,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,To give a calm clear analysis…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:04.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wait. You whipped that act together just yesterday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That is…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:08.94,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Professionalism, Dash. Keep those emotions in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:12.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Overall, it was kinda sorta…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:15.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Overall, it was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Keep working hard, and who knows, you might have a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.38,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Do y'all think she liked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:23.32,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.22,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.30,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,If we keep working hard, we might have a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.52,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So let's keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.45,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Trot to it, ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.80,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Dit you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.58,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm saying this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:36.07,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,they could win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.61,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,But how do we stop them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.91,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,We already called them blank flanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.89,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Then we need to find a new way to get under their skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:52.96,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Or, maybe, get under their wings…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:59.34,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Girls, we just wanted to say your act is quite impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.79,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Wait… What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:02.68,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Um… Thanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.86,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Oh, but of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:06.85,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, we think you're very brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.38,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Brave? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:11.27,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? It is to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.65,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's obvious to everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.58,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,You're showing all three types of Ponyville ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.58,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,yet you have a Pegasus pony…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:21.24,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…who can't even fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.93,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation does that have to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:27.81,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,I'd say not even being able to fly has everything to do with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:28.89,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:32.04,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,I mean, a Pegasus pony at your age?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.51,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,You should've been flying long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:37.48,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So what if my wings can't get me off the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:41.57,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Your career as a flag carrier isn't getting off the ground either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:44.23,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Ms. Harshwhinny will never pick a Pegasus pony
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:48.89,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,who can't fly to represent Ponyville in front of all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:51.79,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Ms. Harshwhinny never said anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.96,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,I would've thought that was obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:56.23,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Well, have fun practicing anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:12:00.44,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,even if your routine will never—how shall I say—take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.94,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to them, Scootaloo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:06.35,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo? You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:09.26,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,This routine isn't working how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.66,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,We've gotta rethink my part in the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.22,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:13.08,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:16.31,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,If we wanna win, I'm gonna have to fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:17.53,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:18.97,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And by tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:21.50,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can win if I work twice as hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.02,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,See? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.05,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Maybe… three times as hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.81,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Golly, I don't know, Scootaloo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.91,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:33.13,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Well I know this for sure – flying is the only way we're gonna win,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:35.13,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,so it's back to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:37.13,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Is this a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.96,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I'll just work four times as hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.75,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:50.25,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Guys, guys, guys! Try it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:54.53,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But we've been rehearsin' all the live long day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:56.05,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We're gettin' tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:59.00,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Fine! We'll skip to my big impressive flying entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.49,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So you've done the doseydo to the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:04.47,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,then to the right, and then there's the hoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.47,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Then I come in-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.99,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Not quite what I had in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:11.41,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,We'll just… try that part again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.94,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I liked the routine the way it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:20.47,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Me too! But all she cares about now is flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:24.98,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll be flying high tomorrow on our final run-through for Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:26.98,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get this, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay, Cutie Mark Crusaders,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:36.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,this is your final run before you show it at the stadium tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:40.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know you're gonna absolutely, positively…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,have a lot of fun, heheh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:51.46,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Ponyville! Home of the…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:53.72,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.08,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Ah, friendship, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:58.27,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Uh, therefore- no, three kinds of ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:01.80,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Left, left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.65,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm just tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:07.31,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And then I dip, and then we turn, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:09.31,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:19.01,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So? What'cha think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:22.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's… y'know… good and all…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:26.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I just thought… maybe possibly you might wanna go back to, say,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:28.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,the first version of the act, which was,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:31.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I dunno, what's the word, better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.54,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just do the routine as it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:35.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with success, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:38.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Seriously. Now I need to…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,go coach these other ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:43.94,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And don't forget, we've got to catch the early train for the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.58,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,See you in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.79,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:49.73,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,We're competing tomorrow, and I still can't fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:51.70,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Unless…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.52,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I'm just too tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:54.90,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I can't keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:15:00.10,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Me too! I'm tired, I'm hungry, and now I hate this routine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.54,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,It feels like it's all about you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:05.64,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,She's right. It's like you don't even need us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:07.51,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Of course, I need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.80,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Without you two, who's gonna hold up the hoop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.43,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Ugh! You don't listen to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.66,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.14,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm going home to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:18.98,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So, are you gonna leave me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.84,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We've gotta catch the early train to the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.67,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I better get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:25.52,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,See you in the morning, Scootaloo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:28.92,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Come on, Scootaloo! Do it for Poniville!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.64,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Just gotta try twenty times as hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:36.39,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Thirty!.. times… as hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:40.70,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Just… a little… harder…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:46.85,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:50.19,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I just… can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:56.11,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Crystal Empire, all aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.75,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.46,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:05.34,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,She better get here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.34,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,This here train is about to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.05,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.19,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We were scared you were gonna miss the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:14.98,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I… I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.10,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.10,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.64,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I'm the weak link.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:23.17,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,If I go, and fall, flop, or do anything but fly, I'm gonna blow it for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.25,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're quitting on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.48,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,But you're better off without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.48,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,But that's not true, Scootaloo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:32.19,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You know what, Sweety Belle? Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:36.36,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,If she's gonna quit, we don't want her, and we don't need her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:37.72,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:39.27,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:40.91,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:43.05,Somepony,,0,0,0,,All aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:02.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,How's my favourite routine going today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:05.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just can't keep it in! I want you to win so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.45,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,…then Scootaloo does that…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,through the hoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.66,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well there ain't gonna be a Scootaloo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.16,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,She's staying home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:16.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:19.42,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,She got in her head that the only way for her to represent Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:21.83,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,is by flying in her routine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:25.04,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,When she couldn't do it, she told us that she was quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And then you tried to stop her from doing that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.33,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Well, actually we kinda told her…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.49,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well, we didn't want a quitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hang on. Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're a team! And a team never leaves a friend behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:48.60,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Sorry you can't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:52.27,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,We'll take a picture for you from the winner's circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.41,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I do not like them one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:57.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Put on some speed, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Throwing away your scooter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:10.61,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:13.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yep! But not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.03,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.90,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And what are they doing here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.12,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,They're supposed to be on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.49,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We're not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:25.54,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Not without you, Scootaloo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:29.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you, Scootaloo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:33.31,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I didn't wanna ruin their chance to win just because I couldn't fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And who said you had to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.97,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,But flying is what pegasus ponies are supposed to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:42.28,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,You flew when you carried the flag in the games.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But that was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.31,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:48.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And it just doesn't matter if you can fly or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:53.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Your routine was amazing cause it represented exactly what makes Ponyville special.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You do still know what that is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.29,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:19:01.30,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Three kinds of ponies living together as friends. Just like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.44,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Earth ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.66,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,unicorns,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.11,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,and pegasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.37,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,But Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.60,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,What if…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.04,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,what if my wings never grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:14.44,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,What if I never fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Listen, Scootaloo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:18.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'll fly someday, or maybe you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:21.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're all kinds of awesome anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:23.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Who's the toughest little pony in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:26.61,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Got the moves, got the mojo…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.65,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,No harder working pony around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.08,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,We are a trio,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.00,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,work as a team
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:39.69,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We'll be the first ponies out on the flag-waving scene
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:43.71,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So let's get to the Crystal Empire and let's do the routine as it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.41,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And let's win this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:50.73,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got hearts as strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:54.62,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got hearts as strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:58.68,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got hearts as strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:02.61,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And we're flying to win as we gallop to glory
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:05.85,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We can conquer any challenge we're in
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:12.32,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've got hearts, hearts strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:16.69,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Hearts strong as horses
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.70,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Ponyville forever! Yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:40.58,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,In the Equestria Games the Ponyville flag will be carried by…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:44.43,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Cutie Mark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:56.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:59.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What you three did was… Acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:02.49,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Acceptable? Acceptable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:08.33,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Why, it was totally, stupendously the single most amazing thing I've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:11.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Contain your excitement, Miss Harshwhinny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:13.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Remember – professionalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.73,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:25.92,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,You know what this means, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:26.67,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:30.09,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,We're totally gonna get cutie marks in flag carrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:31.05,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:36.87,Somepony,,0,0,0,,СЧАСТЛИВЫЙ ПОНЕЦ!
